   "type": "title2",
   "html": "1867 － 1949"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ たからべ・たけし ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n海相、海軍次官、ロンドン軍縮会議全権、海軍大将、<a href=\"../p/ygonnohy.html\">山本権兵衛</a>の女婿"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"04t.html\">一覧　（タ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "hidden"
   },
   "html": "<a name=\"s1\"></a>\n<a href=\"#s1\">＝</a><a href=\"#h\">△</a><a href=\"#h\">◎</a><a href=\"#s2\">▽</a><a href=\"#s1\">＝</a>"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　宮崎県出身。海兵卒。海大卒。日清戦争従軍後、イギリス駐在。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　日露戦争では、大本営作戦参謀を務める。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　海軍次官のとき、<a href=\"../1914/01simen.html\">シーメンス事件</a>が起こり、一時待命となるも復活、海軍大将に昇進。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1922/katoa_1.html\">加藤（友）内閣</a>で海相に就任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　以後、<a href=\"../1923/yamm2_1.html\">山本②</a>、<a href=\"../1924/katob_1.html\">加藤（高）</a>、<a href=\"../1926/waka1_1.html\">若槻①</a>、<a href=\"../p/hosaci.html\">浜口</a>の各内閣で海相を勤める。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　全権として<a href=\"../1930/04londo.html\">ロンドン海軍軍縮条約に調印</a>。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1930/04tosui.html\">統帥権干犯問題</a>など、軍縮反対派の攻撃をうけ<a href=\"../1930/10takar.html\">辞任</a>、予備役に編入される。　"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
